  20 Sep 2007; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> -files/nvidia-2,
  -files/NVIDIA_kernel-2.6.19.patch, files/nvidia,
  nvidia-drivers-1.0.7185.ebuild, -nvidia-drivers-1.0.8776-r1.ebuild,
